\(n\  = \ 10\) , \(y = \frac{83350}{10} = 8335\) ,
\(x = \frac{45}{10} = 4.5\)

\(\widehat{\beta_{1}} = \frac{344,750\ \  - \ \ \frac{45\ *\ 83,350\ }{10}}{285 - \ \ \ \frac{45^{2}}{10}}\ \ \)
\(= \  - \ 367.57\)

\[\widehat{\beta_{0}} = 8335\  + 367.57\ *\ \ 4.5 = 9989.09\]

