7600 \\
7200 \\
\end{pmatrix}\]

\[\begin{pmatrix}
\beta_{0} \\
\beta_{1} \\
\end{pmatrix} = \begin{pmatrix}
9989.09 \\
 - 367.576 \\
\end{pmatrix}\]

So ,linear equation is:

\[\widehat{y_{i}} = \ 9989.09 - 367.576\ x\]

