\includegraphics[width=7in,height=5.25in]{vertopal_949f0de44c59406998abca066c65aa34/media/image18.png}

\protect\hypertarget{_Toc226462975}{}{}Figure : Comparison between three
Models of Cleamed Data without Outlier

\textbf{Comment:}

All three R² values are very high (\textgreater{} 0.94) after removing
the outlier, confirming that it was the primary source of distortion.
The linear model alone explains 94.4\% of the variance.

