\hypertarget{problem-2-heating-oil}{%
\subsection{Problem 2: Heating Oil}\label{problem-2-heating-oil}}

We develop a regression model to estimate heating oil usage for a
single-family home in January, based on two predictors: average
temperature (Temp, in °F) and amount of insulation (Insulation, in
inches).

\hypertarget{dataset-1}{%
\subsubsection{2.1 Dataset}\label{dataset-1}}

\begin{longtable}[]{@{}
  >{\raggedright\arraybackslash}p{(\columnwidth - 4\tabcolsep) * \real{0.3333}}
